<h2>CSS3 Colors</h2>
<p>CSS supports color names, hexadecimal and RGB colors.</p>
<p>In addition, CSS3 also introduces:</p>
<ul>
  <li>RGBA colors</li>
  <li>HSL colors</li>
  <li>HSLA colors</li>
  <li>opacity</li>
</ul>
